==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Samantha'''
# A female [[given name]] of [[American]] origin; the female form of [[Samuel]] (possibly influenced by [[Anthea]])

2. Samantha is a name given to "one born from stardust and filled with light". Anyone who bears this name has extended knowledge in the fields of math and science as well as an active imagination. Anyone named Samantha has supernatural intelectual powers.

